---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/content.css';
---
<BaseLayout title="AI Equipment Planning vs Traditional Methods | Estrelis.ai" description="Compare AI-powered medical equipment planning to traditional manual methods. See how automation, intelligent matching, and real-time collaboration transform healthcare facility planning.">

  <section class="content-hero">
    <h1>AI-Powered vs. Traditional Equipment Planning</h1>
    <p>Traditional equipment planning relies on manual processes, institutional knowledge, and disconnected tools. Estrelis brings AI automation to every step.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>Where Traditional Planning Falls Short</h2>
    <div class="content-grid">
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>Manual Catalog Lookups</h3>
        <p><strong>Traditional:</strong> Planners manually search vendor websites, paper catalogs, and internal databases to find equipment specs and pricing. Hours per item.</p>
        <p><strong>Estrelis:</strong> AI matches imported specs to a centralized catalog instantly. Confidence scores let planners review decisions, not data entry.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>Disconnected Communication</h3>
        <p><strong>Traditional:</strong> Equipment lists travel via email attachments. Architects, planners, and clients work from different versions.</p>
        <p><strong>Estrelis:</strong> Single platform with real-time collaboration. Client portal gives stakeholders direct access. Revit plugin keeps architects in sync.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>Reactive Problem Discovery</h3>
        <p><strong>Traditional:</strong> Discontinued items, budget overruns, and specification conflicts discovered during procurement or installation.</p>
        <p><strong>Estrelis:</strong> AI proactively flags end-of-life products, budget variances, and potential issues during planning — not after purchase orders.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>Knowledge Concentration</h3>
        <p><strong>Traditional:</strong> Equipment expertise lives in individual planners' heads. Team turnover means lost institutional knowledge.</p>
        <p><strong>Estrelis:</strong> AI captures and applies equipment knowledge across the platform. New team members benefit from the full catalog and matching history.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>The Impact of AI Automation</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Equipment matching that took hours now takes minutes</li>
      <li>Discontinued items caught during planning, not procurement</li>
      <li>Budget visibility shifts from monthly reconciliation to real-time</li>
      <li>Client reviews happen in a portal, not email chains</li>
      <li>Field inventory captured digitally instead of on paper</li>
      <li>Institutional knowledge retained in the platform, not just in people</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <h2>See AI-powered planning in action</h2>
    <p>Schedule a demo to see how Estrelis transforms your workflow.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary btn-lg">Request a Demo</a>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
